{"tid":509293,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"林敏聰真係好笑咩","createTime":"2017-12-25T07:15:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T18:55:42.000Z","uid":84511,"like":159,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"f7f87753d4aae1150fa2f705e5ccae7cd6ac60bb","tid":509293,"uid":84511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T07:15:00.000Z","msg":"成日上FACEBOOK見到呢條片<br />\n下面一堆人留言話好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解我完全唔明有咩好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dSLvFC4cc6E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdSLvFC4cc6E&d=tChkqxY43xZa1fhjETCzmmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=f6efb60c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dSLvFC4cc6E</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唯一解釋係佢係無里頭始祖<br />\n睇慣發揚光大後既周星馳<br />\n所以唔覺佢好笑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 林敏聰其他司儀片  不論夾李思捷定白只都完全唔覺好笑"},{"pid":"fb705a742659d447b6e447dbf0e967e98233e564","tid":509293,"uid":48479,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T07:41:46.000Z","msg":"以前開心主流派、上獎門人就好笑嘅，去到大龍鳳茶樓修死皮都還可以<br />\n但而家變咗個煩膠老屎忽"},{"pid":"70281cbc90394ba0846235dfc2abf226be1a9e5e","tid":509293,"uid":80736,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"fb705a742659d447b6e447dbf0e967e98233e564","tid":509293,"uid":48479,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T07:41:46.000Z","msg":"以前開心主流派、上獎門人就好笑嘅，去到大龍鳳茶樓修死皮都還可以<br />\n但而家變咗個煩膠老屎忽"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T07:42:57.000Z","msg":"佢仲可以用「天才」個名呃幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8185a92f76476214a6f8aa178060fbd6e4a8ad7e","tid":509293,"uid":50744,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T07:57:41.000Z","msg":"我覺得可以"},{"pid":"029847a5326ad777ae5549922891c09d1debe52c","tid":509293,"uid":84511,"like":64,"dislike":6,"score":58,"quote":{"pid":"70281cbc90394ba0846235dfc2abf226be1a9e5e","tid":509293,"uid":80736,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"fb705a742659d447b6e447dbf0e967e98233e564","tid":509293,"uid":48479,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T07:41:46.000Z","msg":"以前開心主流派、上獎門人就好笑嘅，去到大龍鳳茶樓修死皮都還可以<br />\n但而家變咗個煩膠老屎忽"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T07:42:57.000Z","msg":"佢仲可以用「天才」個名呃幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T08:02:27.000Z","msg":"我無可否認林敏聰轉數真係快<br />\n但佢轉出黎啲野並唔係話特別幽默<br />\n只係我地估佢唔到 一開始好有新鮮感<br />\n<br />\n睇返樂壇史 佢戈幾首名曲係好有新意<br />\n估唔到歌可以咁樣寫  用一啲平凡字詞表達意思 所以爆紅<br />\n戈陣啲香港人仲係獅子山精神個個無咩學識靠搏殺搵食<br />\n咪覺得呢種風格好好 一方面不失許冠傑既簡單 就連普通賣豬肉佬都聽得明<br />\n另一方面可以表達更抽象既愛情<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到最後<br />\n我地發現佢根本毫無文采毫無才華<br />\n或者講佢自己都知自己根本無料<br />\n就開始扮傻仔 將自己塑造成怪人 鬼才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n為既係大家可以保留以往對佢既評價<br />\n我地諗唔明佢諗乜係我地低級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1564f365818de0dd1f34b3e535fb03c2eecb3e03","tid":509293,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T08:27:28.000Z","msg":"咁佢的確算係半個鬼才嘅<br />\n<br />\n雖然冇張國榮都唔會有佢"},{"pid":"8b0a5a6d3083387d94570b5c46b89dee91ff1fdb","tid":509293,"uid":75235,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T08:28:14.000Z","msg":"戈你老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6074241f4cfa920da2729d5eca1ed591c51a926","tid":509293,"uid":63588,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T08:29:14.000Z","msg":"無可否認佢音樂有d才華<br />\n<br />\n但佢講乜撚我對手喺度就知佢搞笑嗰part已經技窮"},{"pid":"398e2a071e23839b09f72fd27a711c9480431dae","tid":509293,"uid":117837,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T08:29:17.000Z","msg":"你地全部都唔係我對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我對手喺度👐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3207d27dca600c1f280a69dbf90eba9cd16ccc93","tid":509293,"uid":84511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"398e2a071e23839b09f72fd27a711c9480431dae","tid":509293,"uid":117837,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T08:29:17.000Z","msg":"你地全部都唔係我對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我對手喺度👐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T08:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7f15bf8f02717f2871263048f74fe6e84ae91c","tid":509293,"uid":61903,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"398e2a071e23839b09f72fd27a711c9480431dae","tid":509293,"uid":117837,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T08:29:17.000Z","msg":"你地全部都唔係我對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我對手喺度👐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T08:37:46.000Z","msg":"呢個當年中學聽覺得好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cfaa2a55c30da5a7e7db3f1a7c38c93b17c7587","tid":509293,"uid":16272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T08:47:26.000Z","msg":"上遊戲節目真係幾好笑 其他不了"},{"pid":"f87f3745a0c2c8b250f7339ef643c337185c38b0","tid":509293,"uid":141033,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"398e2a071e23839b09f72fd27a711c9480431dae","tid":509293,"uid":117837,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T08:29:17.000Z","msg":"你地全部都唔係我對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我對手喺度👐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T08:51:18.000Z","msg":"其實係表達方法唔掂，如果呢句係農夫講會冇咁突兀<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d35fe4b5dc02bca8681a06088f1384d2d52d006a","tid":509293,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T08:58:08.000Z","msg":"OK啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c09415e4057836551812b57845ccf6e7d802646f","tid":509293,"uid":31215,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"cf7f15bf8f02717f2871263048f74fe6e84ae91c","tid":509293,"uid":61903,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"398e2a071e23839b09f72fd27a711c9480431dae","tid":509293,"uid":117837,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T08:29:17.000Z","msg":"你地全部都唔係我對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我對手喺度👐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T08:37:46.000Z","msg":"呢個當年中學聽覺得好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T08:59:49.000Z","msg":"到而家聽仲覺得好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c1ce155ee6d6fe941ef7808479ab6f11f7df6d","tid":509293,"uid":150400,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T09:06:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff9cea00d5d720921bf491868d8f08ee5a92956d","tid":509293,"uid":85819,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T09:09:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cbb230a4c22c3caca742008f5700c332837ef4de","tid":509293,"uid":84511,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f87f3745a0c2c8b250f7339ef643c337185c38b0","tid":509293,"uid":141033,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"398e2a071e23839b09f72fd27a711c9480431dae","tid":509293,"uid":117837,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T08:29:17.000Z","msg":"你地全部都唔係我對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我對手喺度👐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T08:51:18.000Z","msg":"其實係表達方法唔掂，如果呢句係農夫講會冇咁突兀<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T09:11:42.000Z","msg":"感覺上 農夫會知道呢下係搞緊爛GAG<br />\n而且完全係為左搞笑 平時抽水都輕力抽<br />\n另外 農夫有兩條友 要接爛GAG要打圓場都方便好多 <br />\n<br />\n林敏聰哥PART本身個頭開得奇怪 又成日抽水  係哥個二人環節你會兩個角色有高低之分  鬼才當然係高地位哥個 負責抽人水<br />\n高冷角色突然講個冷笑話就極奇怪<br />\n兩個人都唔識打圓場 哥下咪FAIL<br />\n二人拍擋中要加入冷笑話元素  更加需要技巧 <br />\n場合不同 佢又無農夫既身體語言同裝扮配合 亂講冷笑話咪柒"},{"pid":"b18e1842248b7374c3444b23efb4bd09bc71f679","tid":509293,"uid":150400,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T09:11:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"677d9caeb82fed5d6d58b9720e81b0c26ca0097a","tid":509293,"uid":85819,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T09:13:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1200608801be433bd559c82b813d84d3005c41ee","tid":509293,"uid":153811,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T09:19:55.000Z","msg":"算把啦d廢老廢中，口腦思想簡單。以前有am電波聽到都覺得新奇又有趣，有眼耳口鼻出過下鏡頭係條街見到都覺得人地係寶，林肯聰一早就冇貨賣，玩唔起剩係識黑人面，自己玩人又得，呢d人材簡直<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f9c91aa0224566163bc1cf8b0de6b5fbb374dae","tid":509293,"uid":143582,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8c1ce155ee6d6fe941ef7808479ab6f11f7df6d","tid":509293,"uid":150400,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T09:06:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T09:20:06.000Z","msg":"黃偉文出力都勁過林敏驄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b80d95756cb7c234ad00f730b9e36c595e1a31","tid":509293,"uid":35193,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b18e1842248b7374c3444b23efb4bd09bc71f679","tid":509293,"uid":150400,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T09:11:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T09:20:35.000Z","msg":"On9<br />\n林夕呢啲先叫聰明<br />\n如果唔係點樣撈十幾廿年都仲喺個神枱上面？"},{"pid":"5d